desert fairy circles are considered one of nature 's greatest mysteries . found in namibia , they are large barren patches of earth ringed by short grass dotting the scrub land like craters on the moon , or big freckles . suggestions have included termites nibbling grass , zebras rolling in circles , competition for resources , hydrocarbons emanating from the depths of the earth to kill off patches of vegetation and even aliens .
