kuku kube is available for free on facebook , android , ios and on desktop browsers . on each board , one of the squares is a slightly different shade of the same colour . the aim is to find this odd square by tapping it with your finger or clicking it with the mouse . scores lower than 11 are poor , scores between 15 and 20 is ` lower than average ' , and a score higher than 31 means your eyesight is considered great .
