one in ten of us will develop a kidney stone , and the numbers are rising . they are the result of waste products in the blood forming crystals inside the kidneys , which eventually build up into a solid lump . renal colic is caused by the stone blocking the ureter , the narrow tube that carries urine from the kidney to the bladder .
