researchers in colorado have found evidence for a new solar season cycle . every two years it appears ` bands ' of magnetic field move to the surface . this combines with the existing 11-year solar cycle , causing even more powerful coronal mass ejections -lrb- cmes -rrb- and solar flares that can endanger earth . the study was carried out by a team of researchers led by the national centre for atmospheric research .
